    "strings": [
      "CONFIDENTIAL",
      "Midwest Property & Casualty Group",
      "Karen Weissman, Account Executive",
      "03/15/2026",
      "RE: Buckeye Industrial Properties, LLC \u2014 Transfer Submission",
      "250 Civic Center Drive, Suite 600, Columbus, OH, 43215",
      "To: Underwriting Department, Maine Employers Mutual",
      "Dear Underwriting Team,",
      "Account Overview",
      "We are pleased to submit Buckeye Industrial Properties, LLC for your review and",
      "consideration. The insured is a industrial real estate investment and management \u2014",
      "warehouse, distribution, and light manufacturing facilities throughout Ohio,",
      "headquartered in Columbus, with approximately 31 years of operating history.",
      "Coverage is requested for Commercial Property.",
      "Coverage Requested",
      "Commercial Property: Property coverage on a blanket basis with agreed value",
      "endorsement. Wind/hail deductible applies per schedule.",
      "Loss History Summary",
      "The loss experience reflects a mixed trend with some large individual claims in the",
      "review period. Over the review period, the insured has incurred 2 total claims with",
      "$202,875.00 in total paid losses and $238,554.44 total incurred. Currently, 1 claim",
      "remains open and 1 has been closed.",
      "Annualized loss ratio is 28.1% (avg annual incurred $119,277.22 against current",
      "annual premium $424,883.27 over 2 loss years).",
      "Risk Highlights",
      "\u2022 The insured maintains a formal business continuity and disaster recovery plan",
      "tested annually.",
      "\u2022 An employee assistance program and workplace wellness initiative have been in",
      "place for over five years.",
      "\u2022 All facilities maintain current fire suppression and sprinkler systems inspected",
      "annually by certified contractors.",
      "\u2022 The insured carries contractual risk transfer provisions in all subcontractor and",
      "vendor agreements.",
      "\u2022 All locations are equipped with security camera systems and 24/7 monitoring",
      "services.",
      "\u2022 The insured has implemented a formal return-to-work program that has reduced",
      "lost-time claims by over 30%.",
      "\u2022 The organization has achieved ISO 9001 certification, reflecting a commitment to",
      "quality and process control.",
      "\u2022 31 years of continuous operations under consistent management demonstrates",
      "operational stability.",
      "\u2022 With 95 employees and a structured HR program, the insured maintains low turnover",
      "and consistent safety training.",
      "Broker Recommendation",
      "We believe this account represents a well-managed risk and look forward to establishing a strong partnership.",
      "Please do not hesitate to contact us with any questions or if additional information is required.",
      "Respectfully submitted,",
      "Karen Weissman",
      "Account Executive",
      "Page 1 of 2",
      "Page 2 of 2"
    ],
